hread which extends ClientTransactionHandler. This class represents the main thread of an Android application and is responsible for driving lifecycle transitions by processing ActivityLifecycleItem messages from the ActivityTaskManagerService.\\n\\n3. **ActivityRecord.java** (services/core/java/com/android/server/wm/ActivityRecord.java) - Implements the final class ActivityRecord which extends WindowToken and implements WindowManagerService.AppFreezeListener. This is the server-side representation of an activity in the ActivityTaskManagerService, tracking activity state, configuration, and lifecycle information.\\n\\n4. **ActivityTaskManagerService.java** (services/core/java/com/android/server/wm/ActivityTaskManagerService.java) - Implements the public class ActivityTaskManagerService which extends IActivityTaskManager.Stub. This is the system service that manages activity stacks, tasks, and coordinates lifecycle transitions by sending transaction items to the client-side ActivityThread.\"\n}\n",
